This Resource describes the Properties associated with a person's
blood oxygen saturation level. The spo2 and perfusion Properties are
read-only value that is provided by the server. When range (from
"oic. r. baseresource") is omitted the default is 0 to +MAXFLOAT.
This Property describes the estimation of the oxygen saturation level
This Property describes the ratio of AC over DC of PPG.

against the Properties in the Resource. Thus if a Property is UPDATED
to a value and that Property then RETRIEVED, the RETRIEVED value is
valid if in the range of the set value +/- precision
